      "12": "su de eipas kalws eu se poihsw kai qhsw to sperma sou ws thn ammon ths qalasshs h ouk ariqmhqhsetai apo tou plhqous",
      "13": "kai ekoimhqh ekei thn nukta ekeinhn kai elaben wn eferen dwra kai exapesteilen hsau tw adelfw autou",
