      "28": "eipen de autw ou klhqhsetai eti to onoma sou iakwb alla israhl estai to onoma sou oti eniscusas meta qeou kai meta anqrwpwn dunatos",
      "29": "hrwthsen de iakwb kai eipen anaggeilon moi to onoma sou kai eipen ina ti touto erwtas to onoma mou kai huloghsen auton ekei",
