      "25": "egeneto de en th hmera th trith ote hsan en tw ponw elabon oi duo uioi iakwb sumewn kai leui oi adelfoi dinas ekastos thn macairan autou kai eishlqon eis thn polin asfalws kai apekteinan pan arsenikon",
