      "30": "eipen de iakwb sumewn kai leui mishton me pepoihkate wste ponhron me einai pasin tois katoikousin thn ghn en te tois cananaiois kai tois ferezaiois egw de oligostos eimi en ariqmw kai sunacqentes ep eme sugkoyousin me kai ektribhsomai egw kai o oikos mou",
